text: what the fuck... has marrow gnawer always been the #1 mono black commander?
that does seem strange
top 3 look close
i just posted some stats in general
i thought it might have been some Greek Brago Guy type shenanigans but it all seems normal
gotta rack up the Zo-Zu the punisher numbers
<makes ten zozu decks)
so I’ve tested the homepage using an EU VPN across multiple browsers (chrome, firefox focus, safari) on mac os, iOS, and android and they all work fine
getting the nitro ads banner and everything
his android phone must be older because I don’t even have a “default android web browser”
if I wanted to test older OSes I could try setting up a virtual phone in xcode but it’s a nontrivial amount of time
for the record, firefox focus does block ads by default, apparently it’s a privacy-focused browser
but still everything worked fine
i have no idea then, you looked into this more than i expected you to
if it were on desktop we could probably ask him to send us his console output
doing that from mobile is a pain
the only thing that gave me concern was i thought it had something to do with the ad thing and since it was europe maybe nobody else has complained
but im confortable saying this is a personal problem on his end
aight

1. Return a full list of recs.  I wont load them all at once on the client-side, but they will show up as the user scrolls down, or maybe a "show more" link like there is on recs right now
